{"tid":1050084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"漢堡塔羅占卜（2）開左個ig","createTime":"2019-03-06T17:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T04:10:09.000Z","uid":38191,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d31a746e7735b1e880b027c9ef99f45f699f95cb","tid":1050084,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:50:17.000Z","msg":"加番d規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nxx運會點，幾時xxxx<br />\n幾時出pool/身邊有無人鍾意你/有無人同你有機會/幾時女（男）朋友會出現/幾時會有人鍾意我<br />\n<br />\n以上問題全部唔占<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次玩唔知點問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愛情問：<br />\n對象對我有咩看法<br />\n同曖昧對象有無機會<br />\n有無機會複合<br />\n同男女朋友會唔會長久<br />\n工作問：<br />\n應唔應該轉工<br />\n自己適合咩工作<br />\n<br />\n每人限問一條<br />\n<br />\n之前問過果d可以再搵我占啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常我準備占你果陣會hi 你，你見到可以覆下我，我要確保你知道我占緊你我先會開牌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無格式需要，你覺得重要就同我講，通常留性別同問題就得<br />\n<br />\n通常開1張/3張<br />\n<br />\n想認真仔細占/瘋狂發問可以考慮下課金<br />\n<br />\nIG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/burgertarot?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=1h3hn9s9lnzem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fburgertarot%3Futm_source%3Dig_profile_share%26igshid%3D1h3hn9s9lnzem&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=df450938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/burgertarot?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=1h3hn9s9lnzem</a><br />\n<br />\nTG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/godstickburger\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgodstickburger&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=16dbe9a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/godstickburger</a><br />\n<br />\n老規矩只回TG/IG"},{"pid":"9eead59022d626c9a5338867314f6e6f58bcb9ff","tid":1050084,"uid":38191,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:51:33.000Z","